\s Nikipata ulimwengu wote
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Nikipata ulimwengu wote,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Na kukosa Yesu Mukombozi, Sitakua na furaha kamwe,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Vitu vya dunia hii ni bule\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Nikipata ulimwengu wote,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Na kukosa Yesu Mukombozi, Nitakuwa na huzuni sana, Yesu pekee anafurahisha.\bd*
